车就是比自己的香。马斯克解释称，这是因为去年 12 月特斯拉才继续取得了进展，在生产速度加快以后，特斯拉发现问题的速度也加快了。 马斯克还自曝：「早期的 Model S 座椅可能是我坐过的所有汽车中最差的。」"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-195b572e9f741799d121bbc35e528d3c_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "94 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/442819243"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IgNKbx7HutLh3EAMaCDYwNjgyMTMyIKaO7oAGMAE4UUAlcgk0NDI4MTkyNDN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1612497957.022314", "card_id": "Q_442701602", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 35}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待曲玮玮采访中，76 年高管母亲「培养孩子没有上限」的教育理念？给年轻父母了哪些启示？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "作家曲玮玮最近采访了一位 76 年的企业高管妈妈，看到她打算花 1000 万在孩子的培养上，普通人根本不敢想吧。而且这 1000 万还不是乱花的，教育、娱乐、生活、兴趣都规划了进去，并称「培养孩子没有上限」。对于这样的教育理念你怎么看？这会不会限制了孩子的自由？如果没有那么多钱要怎样规划为孩子规划其方方面面？预算和规划的度在哪里呢？微博"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "78 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/442701602"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IgNKbx7HutLh3EAMaCDYwNjU1OTQ3IIiG6oAGMAE4eUAmcgk0NDI3MDE2MDJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1612497957.0227823", "card_id": "Q_343563096", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 724}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "请问您听过最惊艳的三行情书是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-cd7dddc82ee4492a1e14a6370702dff9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "73 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/343563096"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgNKbx7HutLh3EAMaCDM4NjI0MTU5IMeuo+sFMAg4lyxAJ3IJMzQzNTYzMDk2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1612497957.0230758", "card_id": "Q_437789442", "f